<title>ṭwby̱ lly ạ̹tẖmh ạtgẖfr</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - ṭwby̱ lly ạ̹tẖmh ạtgẖfr wạlkẖṭyẗ ạtstrt
 mḥfwẓ m ạlnạr wạlkẖṭr wạlkẖṭyẗ ʿbrt
 1- ạṣbḥ mn ạ̉wlạd ạllh lyh fy ạlạbn ḍmạn
 wḥyạẗ
 wạlrwḥ ạlqdws jwạh byʿrfh kl mạ llh
 2- ạtḥrr bʿd ạlgẖfrạn wạtbrr ʿạysẖ fy ạ̉mạn
 wạlsẖyṭạn mạlhwsẖ slṭạn ạṣlh dạ mn ạ̉wlạd ạllh
 3- kl mạ llh ạ̉ṣbḥ lyh wlạ sẖyʾ m ạldynwnẗ
 ʿlyh
 wạlwʿd ạlmḍmwn fy ạ̹ydyh m ạlbryẗ lḥd smạh
 4- mrḍy ʿnh fy ạlmsyḥ mtgẖṭy bdm ạldẖbyḥ
 yḥly̱ lh ạlgẖnạ wạltsbyḥ wạltmjyd lạsm ạllh</lyrics>
</song>